Almost everyone likes burger. In fact, people are ready to cover a long distance to satisfy their tasting buds. You maintain a popular food truck in a big city of the USA and the major responsibility you have to carry here is to get the appetites of your customers satisfied. Make sure that you will do the job fast and leave all your customers with a smile on their faces. Take their orders timely and, they will give you good money in a return. You are going to have huge fun in this exciting and highly challenging free online cooking game – Burger Truck Frenzy USA.  

Begin this cool html5 game with collecting all the useful ingredients that you will see on the screen. Proper burger recipes are available there to help you out. Follow it properly to prepare a delicious burger for your customers. Collect the coins for completing your order successfully. You will be able to gather extra coins from your every happy customer in this brand new cooking game for girls and boys. We focus on the details and play this best girl cooking game with confidence since unhappy customers leave your shop without paying anything to you.  

The job is really difficult for you, but paying attention to all the useful instructions and indications will definitely help you get through all the hurdles that you may face during the completion of all 30 stages. Use your cooking skills and show the world that you are truly a food truck champion. No need to bother if the result doesn’t come in the first attempt. You are free her to play this best kids game again and again in your browser. Good luck friends to rock today by beating all your previous score in your favorite free online cooking games!
